{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "mediconnect-full-rbac-id",
        "name": "Mediconnect Full RBAC Matrix",
        "description": "Collection COMPLÈTE testant la matrice de sécurité pour ADMIN, DOCTOR, et PATIENT.\n\n### Matrice Testée :\n\n| Endpoint | Method | ADMIN | DOCTOR | PATIENT |\n| :--- | :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: |\n| /auth/ | ALL | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| /api/patients | GET | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| /api/patients | POST | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| /api/patients/{id} | PUT/DEL | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| /api/patients/me | GET | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |\n| /api/doctors | GET | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| /api/doctors | POST/PUT/DEL | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| /api/rendezvous | POST | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| /api/rendezvous/me | GET | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |\n| /api/factures | GET | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| /api/factures | POST | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |\n| /api/factures/{id}/payer | PUT | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "item": [
